  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 revision)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This revision elevates the Model Risk Level to 3 reflecting increased regulatory scrutiny and broader intended use scope. The assessment retains the 7-factor evaluated core but leaves three factors unassessed, characterised as beyond the current project scope without concrete justification for why their absence is acceptable at MRL 3.",
